videos.headline: Kennesaw State wins ASUN tournament to earn first NCAA tournament bid
videos.description: After Liberty's Colin Porter hits a game-tying 3-pointer, Terrell Burden draws a foul in the final second and hits the go-ahead free throw to send Kennesaw State dancing.
